text:
```Data:

&lt;someVideo&gt; a app:Video;
  app:subtitles "en" , "es" ;
  app:enncoding "av1", "vp6" ;
  app:container "avi", "mp4" .

Query:

SELECT ?video
WHERE { 
  ?video app:subtitles ?anything ;
         app:encoding "h.263", "mp4" .
}```

